OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FWhile some might think it's "rain,
OL,8,Frain go away", the reality should be
OL,9,Ffar from it.
OL,11,FAfter one of the driest and warmest
OL,12,Fsprings on record, rain has finally
OL,13,Freturned to many parts of the UK this
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,16,FIt gives us all a chance to make small
OL,17,Fpreparations for what experts are
OL,18,Falready warning could be a hotter and
OL,19,Fdrier than average summer.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@MO]
