OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FSo, here's how we can make the most of
OL,8,Fit.
OL,10,FWhy are water companies already asking
OL,11,Fpeople to save water?
OL,13,FThe recent record-breaking hot spell
OL,14,Fhas put increasing pressure on water
OL,15,Fsupplies, which, coupled with a drier-
OL,16,Fthan-average spring, has led to some
OL,17,Fsuppliers already sounding the warning
OL,18,Fbells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
