OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780582264
OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FDemand increased by up to 50 per cent
OL,8,Fin some areas during last week's
OL,9,Fheatwave, according to Thames Water.
OL,11,FWith leaks increasing during hot, dry
OL,12,Fspells due to cracking ground, the
OL,13,Fwater company has urged customers to
OL,14,Fuse water wisely.
OL,16,FWhy is this week's rainfall important?
OL,18,FIt was an exceptionally dry spring,
OL,19,Fwith the south and southeast seeing
OL,20,Fonly a third of their expected rain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
