OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FAlthough this week's rain is welcome,
OL,8,Fexperts say it will take more than a
OL,9,Ffew wet days to make up for such a
OL,10,Fsignificant dry spell.
OL,12,FWhile heavy rain can temporarily
OL,13,Freplenish rivers and reservoirs, much
OL,14,Fof the water can be lost through rapid
OL,15,Frunoff if the ground is very dry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
