OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FMany rivers, reservoirs and
OL,8,Fgroundwater sources remain below where
OL,9,Fthey would normally be at this point
OL,10,Fin the year, so this week's much-
OL,11,Fneeded rain could be an opportunity
OL,12,Ffor households to store water and
OL,13,Fimprove their resilience before the
OL,14,Fnext period of dry weather arrives.
OL,16,FHow much hotter and drier will this
OL,17,Fsummer be?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
