OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FThe Met Office says it is twice as
OL,8,Flikely that the UK will experience a
OL,9,Fwarmer-than-average summer, with an
OL,10,Fincreased chance of heatwaves.
OL,12,FIts long-range forecast suggests
OL,13,Ftemperatures are likely to rise above
OL,14,Faverage through much of June, with
OL,15,Fperiods of dry, settled weather
OL,16,Fdeveloping.
OL,18,FWhat are the public being advised to
OL,19,Fdo to prepare for a dry summer?
OL,21,FWhat is a water butt?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
