PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780582264
OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FA water butt is a container that
OL,8,Fcollects and stores rainwater from a
OL,9,Froof via a home's guttering system.
OL,11,FThis can be used to water gardens,
OL,12,Fflower beds, hanging baskets and
OL,13,Fvegetable patches during dry weather.
OL,15,FHouseholds can reduce demand on public
OL,16,Fwater supplies while potentially
OL,17,Fsaving money by using rainwater
OL,18,Finstead of treated drinking water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
