PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780582264
OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FWater butts are widely available from
OL,8,Fgarden centres and DIY retailers, but
OL,9,Fit's worth checking locally as some
OL,10,Fcouncils and water companies offer
OL,11,Fdiscounted schemes.
OL,13,FHow much water can a water butt save?
OL,15,FA typical water butt holds around 200
OL,16,Flitres, which is enough to fill more
OL,17,Fthan 20 watering cans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
