PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780582264
OL,3,CWhy this week's rain is so important
OL,4,Cand how to make the most of it for
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FAre there any other ways to make the
OL,8,Fmost of this week's rain?
OL,10,FWhile this week's rain may not be
OL,11,Fwelcomed by everyone, every drop could
OL,12,Fprove valuable after one of the driest
OL,13,Fsprings on record.
OL,15,FWith the prospect of further hot
OL,16,Fweather later this summer, simple
OL,17,Factions like filling a water butt
OL,18,Fcould mean having hundreds of litres
OL,19,Fof free water available when gardens -
OL,20,Fand water supplies - come under
OL,21,Fpressure again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
